    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地狱卡牌 II》是一款既可单人游玩、也可最多 4 人联机的合作 roguelike 牌组构建游戏。游戏舞台依旧设定在《地狱卡牌》与恶魔之书中熟悉的纸地下城世界，并拓展出全新生态区域与故事线；你将在翻页般的冒险中一路下潜，迎战邪恶大军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/31d827780414ff79570fd1671d11340f.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/31d827780414ff79570fd1671d11340f.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/31d827780414ff79570fd1671d11340f.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这里没有纯装饰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地狱卡牌 II》延续了前作扎实的牌组构建核心，并在此基础上加入了角色属性系统，以及更深入的长期成长内容：装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备既会改变英雄外观，也会实打实地影响你的战斗表现！ 它会同时调整你的牌组、属性数值与增益效果。你看到的每一次“换装”，都会带来玩法层面的变化，让你从开局就能按自己偏好的套路去构筑与成型。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/cf8d4df4c7dbce9cac1e61a43de34539.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/cf8d4df4c7dbce9cac1e61a43de34539.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/cf8d4df4c7dbce9cac1e61a43de34539.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/08738b81bd39c3897f1c0ee1b6148077.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/08738b81bd39c3897f1c0ee1b6148077.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/08738b81bd39c3897f1c0ee1b6148077.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >看清你脚下的位置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地狱卡牌 II》之所以与大多数牌组构建游戏不同，是因为这里怪物的站位真的重要，而且能被你利用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人会处在近战或远程的不同位置，并在英雄之间形成对位与分区；你如何分配目标、如何把敌人留在合适的位置，都会直接影响连击是否成立、爆发能否打满。站位不是细节，而是你打出最强连招的关键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/d9f0a57d613c409acf0d6d9689f3e697.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/d9f0a57d613c409acf0d6d9689f3e697.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/d9f0a57d613c409acf0d6d9689f3e697.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友并肩谋划，或独自统领全队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地狱卡牌 II》支持最多 4 名英雄协同作战，共同迎战巨龙威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单人模式中，你将同时操控整支队伍，所有出牌与战术都由你一手决定，你就像独行侠一样，掌握一整个队伍的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多人模式中，你可以与好友或陌生队友配合，协同站位与出牌节奏，击溃蜂拥而来的敌群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/6485ba5349b4fde1faa2175f8a1a0164.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/6485ba5349b4fde1faa2175f8a1a0164.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/6485ba5349b4fde1faa2175f8a1a0164.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >展开故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次冒险都独一无二，故事也会随着你的推进不断演化。集结伙伴、整备装备、守护王国，一步步揭开龙之灾厄背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/fd24b5bc519f3bbe6e4f964bfaca6a1a.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/fd24b5bc519f3bbe6e4f964bfaca6a1a.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/fd24b5bc519f3bbe6e4f964bfaca6a1a.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对《地狱卡牌 II》感兴趣，欢迎在 Steam 上把它加入愿望单。 就算还在观望也不妨先点一下：也许我们会给你一个惊喜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/8adf4f10b72c59306d446a4744dc6847.poster.avif?t=1770408453\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/8adf4f10b72c59306d446a4744dc6847.webm?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/8adf4f10b72c59306d446a4744dc6847.mp4?t=1770408453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《回归游戏》系列简介</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/db580726166cc4583ed9e039e9a3a1ea.avif?t=1770408453\" width=600 height=194 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《回归游戏》</strong>作为一个中核游戏系列，灵感源自电脑端游戏的黄金时代。《回归游戏》的每一部作品都会致敬1990年代的一部热门游戏，利用现代的手段，依靠创新且通常大幅简化的游戏机制，以新的形式将一个故事呈现在全新的受众面前。最初，我们只是打算将《地狱卡牌》作为新的模式，加入《回归游戏》系列第一部作品<strong>《恶魔之书》</strong>，不过后来很快发现我们的构思远非一个“模式”那么简单，因而决定将其作为独立的衍生游戏推出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106270/extras/d6f9a2efcc97dd34c1f415fe093a5ab5.avif?t=1770408453\" width=600 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想进一步了解《回归游戏》这个系列，或者想支持我们开发这个系列，请前往<strong>“支持礼包”</strong>商店页面。<strong>《地狱卡牌》</strong>发行之后，也会加入其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
